      "name": "Weight Change Goals",
      "code": "PX230701",
      "abbreviation": "PX230701",
      "description": "This is a two-item measure of an individual’s weight change goals used in the 2015 Youth Risk Behavior Survey (YRBS).",
      "domain": "Self & Coping",
      "citation": "Brener, N. D., Kann, L., McManus, T., Kinchen, S. A., Sundberg, E. C., & Ross, J. G. (2002). The reliability of the 1999 Youth Risk Behavior Survey Questionnaire. Journal of Adolescent Health, 1 (4), 336-342. Bish, C.L., Blanck, H.M., Serdula, MK., Marcus, M., Kohl, HW 3 rd , Kahn, LK. (2005). Diet and physical activity behaviors among Americans trying to lose weight: 2000 Behavioral Risk Factor Surveillance System. Obesity Research, Mar; 13(3): 596-607. [PhenX: https://www.phenxtoolkit.org/protocols/view/230701]",
